---
/**
 * Cztery audyty: 3 darmowe self-serve w grid 3-col + 1 płatny pełnoszerokie.
 * Inspirowane kahena.com/ai-bot-tester (AI bots) + powerdigitalmarketing services.
 */
---

<section class="relative w-full" style="background: var(--bg);" id="audyty" aria-labelledby="audyty-title">
  <div class="content-container py-20 lg:py-28">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <span class="meta mb-4 inline-block">Co dostajesz</span>
      <h2
        id="audyty-title"
        class="text-ink font-display mt-2 mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        Trzy darmowe testy i&nbsp;jeden pełny audyt
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ink text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Zacznij od&nbsp;trzech bezpłatnych testów &ndash; bez logowania, bez zapłaty.
        Gdy zobaczysz wyniki, decydujesz, czy chcesz pełny raport z&nbsp;planem działania.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid 3 darmowych testów -->
    <div class="mb-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-7">

      <!-- 01 – Brand check -->
      <article
        id="brand-check"
        class="border-rule bg-bg-card relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 lg:p-7"
      >
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[color:var(--accent-edge)] bg-[color:var(--accent-soft)] px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
            Darmowe · instant
          </span>
          <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">01 / 04</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] lg:text-[1.375rem]">
          Co AI wie o&nbsp;Twojej marce
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ink-soft mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Odpytujemy ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini i&nbsp;Perplexity o&nbsp;Twoją firmę.
          Dostajesz sentyment, listę halucynacji i&nbsp;konkurentów, których AI poleca zamiast Ciebie.
        </p>

        <!-- Mock UI compact – 4 LLM x status -->
        <div class="border-rule bg-bg mb-5 rounded-xl border p-4" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="text-ink-mute mb-3 flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">
            <span>acme.pl</span>
            <span class="text-accent">● live</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5">
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px]">
              <span class="text-ink">ChatGPT</span>
              <span class="text-accent">Myli ofertę</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px]">
              <span class="text-ink">Claude</span>
              <span class="text-ink-mute">Brak danych</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px]">
              <span class="text-ink">Gemini</span>
              <span class="text-accent">Poleca konkurenta</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px]">
              <span class="text-ink">Perplexity</span>
              <span class="text-ink-soft">Zna · neutralny</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA pinned bottom -->
        <a
          class="text-accent hover:text-[color:var(--accent-bright)] mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase transition"
          href="/narzedzia/brand-check"
          aria-label="Sprawdź, co AI wie o Twojej marce – darmowe"
        >
          Sprawdź markę <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- 02 – URL check -->
      <article
        id="url-check"
        class="border-rule bg-bg-card relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 lg:p-7"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[color:var(--accent-edge)] bg-[color:var(--accent-soft)] px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
            Darmowe · instant
          </span>
          <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">02 / 04</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] lg:text-[1.375rem]">
          Czy Twój content jest cytowalny
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ink-soft mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Wskazujesz jeden URL. Score 0&ndash;100 + lista 5 priorytetowych zmian
          według badań Princeton i&nbsp;Indig (1.2M&nbsp;cytowań ChatGPT).
        </p>

        <!-- Mock UI compact – score + 3 progress bars -->
        <div class="border-rule bg-bg mb-5 rounded-xl border p-4" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="text-ink-mute mb-2 truncate font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">
            /blog/jak-wybrac-saas
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-baseline gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent font-display text-[2.75rem] leading-none font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em]">43</span>
            <span class="text-ink-soft text-base">/ 100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1.5 font-mono text-[10px]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-20 truncate">Front-load</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 78%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-20 truncate">Schema</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 25%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-20 truncate">Cytowania</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 12%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          class="text-accent hover:text-[color:var(--accent-bright)] mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase transition"
          href="/narzedzia/url-check"
          aria-label="Sprawdź content jednego URL – darmowe"
        >
          Sprawdź URL <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- 03 – AI bots check (NOWY, wzór kahena) -->
      <article
        id="ai-bots-check"
        class="border-rule bg-bg-card relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 lg:p-7"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[color:var(--accent-edge)] bg-[color:var(--accent-soft)] px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
            Darmowe · instant
          </span>
          <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">03 / 04</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] lg:text-[1.375rem]">
          Czy AI ma dostęp do&nbsp;Twojej strony
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ink-soft mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Sprawdzamy <code class="text-ink font-mono text-xs">robots.txt</code>: czy GPTBot,
          ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot, Google-Extended i&nbsp;9&nbsp;innych botów AI mają w&nbsp;ogóle wstęp
          na&nbsp;Twoją stronę.
        </p>

        <!-- Mock UI compact – tabela botów -->
        <div class="border-rule bg-bg mb-5 rounded-xl border p-4" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">acme.pl/robots.txt</span>
            <span class="text-ink font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold">
              <span class="text-accent">8</span> / 13 dopuszczonych
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1 font-mono text-[11px]">
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ink">GPTBot</span>
              <span class="text-accent" aria-label="dopuszczony">✓</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ink">ClaudeBot</span>
              <span class="text-ink-mute" aria-label="zablokowany">✗</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ink">PerplexityBot</span>
              <span class="text-accent" aria-label="dopuszczony">✓</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ink">Google-Extended</span>
              <span class="text-ink-mute" aria-label="zablokowany">✗</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ink">CCBot</span>
              <span class="text-ink-mute" aria-label="zablokowany">✗</span>
            </li>
            <li class="text-ink-mute pt-1 text-[10px]">+&nbsp;8 innych botów</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <a
          class="text-accent hover:text-[color:var(--accent-bright)] mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase transition"
          href="/narzedzia/ai-bots-check"
          aria-label="Sprawdź dostęp botów AI do Twojej strony – darmowe"
        >
          Sprawdź dostęp <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>

    </div>

    <!-- 04 – Pełny audyt (paid, full-width premium banner) -->
    <article
      id="pelny-audyt"
      class="bg-bg-card relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16"
      style="border-color: var(--accent-edge); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-edge), 0 16px 48px var(--accent-glow);"
    >
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 -left-32 h-80 w-80 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,106,46,0.22) 0%, transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,138,79,0.14) 0%, transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Copy -->
        <div>
          <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-ink inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-rule bg-bg-elevated px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Płatne · 3 dni
            </span>
            <span class="text-accent font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">★ Polecane</span>
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">04 / 04</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.5rem] lg:leading-[1.05]">
            Pełny audyt z&nbsp;planem działania na&nbsp;90&nbsp;dni
          </h3>
          <p class="text-ink mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed sm:text-lg">
            30&ndash;50 priorytetowych zapytań z&nbsp;Twojej branży × 5&nbsp;wyszukiwarek AI.
            Share of Voice vs&nbsp;konkurencja, audyt techniczny pod AI&nbsp;crawlery, mapa luk
            tematycznych i&nbsp;30/60/90-dniowa roadmapa wdrożenia.
          </p>

          <ul class="text-ink-soft mb-8 space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Raport PDF (40&ndash;60&nbsp;stron) + dashboard z&nbsp;danymi
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Lista 20+ konkretnych zmian na stronie z&nbsp;priorytetem
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              60-min sesja prezentacji wyników z&nbsp;ekspertem ICEA
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Schema.org, llms.txt i&nbsp;quick-wins do&nbsp;wdrożenia od&nbsp;ręki
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
            <a class="btn-primary" href="/kontakt?type=full-audit" aria-label="Zamów pełny audyt widoczności AI">
              Zamów pełny audyt &rarr;
            </a>
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              od&nbsp;6&nbsp;900&nbsp;PLN
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mock UI – PDF report preview + SoV chart -->
        <div
          class="border-rule bg-bg relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 sm:p-7"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <div class="text-ink-mute mb-4 flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">
            <span>Raport · podgląd</span>
            <span class="text-accent">● PDF · 47 stron</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-5">
            <div class="text-ink-mute mb-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Share of Voice · acme.pl vs konkurencja
            </div>
            <div class="text-ink font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em]">
              18.4<span class="text-ink-soft text-xl">%</span>
              <span class="text-accent ml-3 font-mono text-xs">↗ +6.2pp potencjał</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Bar chart mock -->
          <div class="space-y-2.5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-24 truncate">Konkurent A</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-soft h-full rounded-full" style="width: 32%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-12 text-right">32.1%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-24 truncate">Konkurent B</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-soft h-full rounded-full" style="width: 24%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-12 text-right">24.7%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink w-24 truncate font-semibold">acme.pl</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 18.4%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink w-12 text-right font-semibold">18.4%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-24 truncate">Konkurent C</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-soft h-full rounded-full" style="width: 14%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-12 text-right">14.2%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-mute w-24 truncate">Pozostali</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-mute/40 h-full rounded-full" style="width: 10%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-mute w-12 text-right">10.6%</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Action items -->
          <div class="border-rule mt-5 border-t pt-4">
            <div class="text-ink-mute mb-2 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Roadmapa · 23 action items
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1.5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                <span class="text-accent">P0</span>
                <span class="text-ink-soft truncate">Schema FAQ na 12 podstronach kategorii</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                <span class="text-accent">P0</span>
                <span class="text-ink-soft truncate">Pillar /porownanie-[marka]-vs-konkurencja</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                <span class="text-accent">P1</span>
                <span class="text-ink-soft truncate">Wikidata + Wikipedia onboarding</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px]">
                + 20 więcej w&nbsp;raporcie
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>
